Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:28.49,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是不是不可能的嘛
Comment: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:30.33,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.67,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直響著的沉默的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是誰的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:56.49,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳進去跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:58.85,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起來 破壞掉這無理的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:00.44,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不開這沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.86,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.19,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到終幕我都要說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.06,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 這不是玩笑
Comment: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Nighty night
Comment: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:11.60,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:14.12,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}去捨棄掉吧 rulers
Comment: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:15.95,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.04,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}One day…
Comment: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.56,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,波打つざわめき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:36.08,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,彩度を失う記憶に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.67,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,願いは幾度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.43,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,数えてみたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.12,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,震えている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.90,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,晦冥を揺らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:52.14,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,希望に似てた歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:55.76,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,祈れば砂のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:59.29,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,零れ落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.96,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:06.35,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,密かに息吹く想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:10.14,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた鋼に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:14.37,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,意味もなく　際限なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:16.28,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,廻るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:21.06,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,世界が引き裂かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.79,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,結んだ手離さずいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:29.22,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,歪んだ支配が朽ちても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:30.90,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,その名を呼ぶの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:34.93,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,綺麗なアイじゃなくっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:38.88,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,息をするたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:42.94,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,あなた求めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:47.17,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,どこへはぐれてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:49.41,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.56,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,起起落落的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:36.08,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,在失去色彩的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.67,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈求了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.43,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,只是數一數
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.12,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,也混身震顫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.90,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,像是那波動黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:52.14,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,希望似的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:55.76,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈禱的話就會像沙礫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:59.29,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,凋零飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.96,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我一直都知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:06.35,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,那呼吸中不為人知的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:10.14,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,接觸到了生鏽的鋼鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:14.37,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,沒有意義 沒有終點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:16.28,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,循環
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:21.06,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算世界崩裂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.79,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我們握緊的手也不會分開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:29.22,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算扭曲的統治腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:30.90,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我也會呼喚那個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:34.93,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算不是美麗的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:38.88,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我只要一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:42.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,便在尋求著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:47.17,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,無論迷失在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:49.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,再一次
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
